column5: well gang after a long period i owe thanks to eh and the bosses of the site. happy new year.
Well, it's about time! I've been seeing more and more of your creations in the GLA (Greater Lambeth Area!) Hope business is going well and maybe see you again this opener. -Brian
Good to have you back George, it's been a long time bud !!
thanks guys. i have been busy.. lew hows my buddy marvin
Marvin's doing very well George, thanks for asking, but you still can't use him for bait
Well welcome back it shure did not take long to get on the marv track again Lew your smart to leave him at home for the trips here
Good to see you on the board again George !

Hey Cuz!!  Good to see ya back!!!!  If you were having trouble with the computer you know I am just down the street, give me a call!!!  Hope you and Nora had a wonderful holiday!!!  I will be seeing you soon for some baits to go on the fly in that Dad and I are going on in the spring.....gotta show the northern folks some southern Woodies!!!!   Chrispy!
hi george  thought you would like to know i took a 20lb salmon on a 6 inch blue/black jointed 110 ft down off the rigger last august
